title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 11, Appendices, app 25E - Authority of the Superintendent

N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. tit. 11, Appendices, app 25E - Authority of the Superintendent

State Regulations

The rates of mortality in Tables 1 - 40 of this Appendix are per 1,000 lives. Tables for both Age Nearest Birthday (ANB) and Age Last Birthday (ALB) have been provided for Super Preferred Nonsmoker, Preferred Nonsmoker, Residual Standard Nonsmoker, Preferred Smoker, and Residual Standard Smoker based on Select and Ultimate (S&U) and Ultimate Only (Ult) for both Male (M) and Female (F) lives.
